{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# High-End Quantum AI Multi-Agent Trading Architecture\nGenerated: 2026-05-06\n\nTarget: automated Indian-market trading platform using local Gemma-compatible LLM agents, neural/deep learning models, quantum-assisted optimization, multi-agent RL research, deterministic risk controls, and a 5 crore/year aspirational profit-goal governor.\n\nImportant: this optimizes risk-adjusted decision quality. It cannot guarantee profit.",
      "x": -4200,
      "y": -1200,
      "width": 3300,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "profit_goal",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Profit Goal Reality Layer\n\n5 crore/year is a target constraint, not a promise.\n\nThe system tracks:\n- yearly target and run-rate\n- capital required estimate\n- drawdown budget\n- probability of target under Monte Carlo\n- strategy contribution\n\nGoal pressure may increase research and validation intensity, but never overrides risk, compliance, broker controls, or kill switch.",
      "x": -700,
      "y": -1200,
      "width": 2300,
      "height": 310,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "model_stack",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## High-End Model Stack\n\nLocal LLM agent layer:\n- Gemma 4 31B Dense: chief analyst, strategy review, research synthesis\n- Gemma 4 26B MoE: lower-latency desk coordinator\n- Gemma 4 E4B/E2B: fast local micro-agents\n- optional external Claude/GPT only for offline review, never required for live trading\n\nNeural/deep learning layer:\n- Temporal Fusion Transformer / PatchTST / N-BEATS / LSTM ensemble\n- GNN for cross-asset correlation and sector contagion\n- autoencoder anomaly detection\n- deep volatility and tail-risk models\n- multi-agent RL policies trained only in simulation\n\nQuantum layer:\n- QUBO/CQM portfolio selection\n- Qiskit VQE/QAOA research lane\n- D-Wave hybrid CQM/BQM lane\n- quantum kernels for shadow regime classification",
      "x": 1800,
      "y": -1200,
      "width": 3100,
      "height": 470,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
